            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I suspect this applies to any `cdef class` - if we were to do it I doubt that it should be specific to dataclasses.\r\n\r\nObviously there's the usual caveat that `cdef classes` trade some convenience for efficiency so not everything that works for a regular class is necessarily expected to work for them.",
