        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "You're right (about it applying to any cdef class), I just adapted/checked the above example to confirm locally. \r\n\r\nInterestingly, in my case, the reason I hit this is because `pdoc` was failing horribly just for dataclasses, not for other cython cclasses.  This turns out to be because it has a special branch in the code for dataclasses (not because of cython treating dataclasses differently)\r\n\r\nWould be a big nice-to-have, but I can see that I hit a corner-case here.",
